<TITLE> Man gets 30 years for raping 4 yr old </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, May 20 (bdnews24.com)  A Dhaka court on Thursday sentenced a man to 30 years in prison for raping a four-year old girl in Dhaka. The convicted was identified as Abdul Samad, son of Bazlu Mia of Choddokhola (cluster village) of Saturia upazila in Manikganj. Dhaka's Women and Children Repression Prevention Tribunal judge Bimal Chandra Sikder gave the verdict on Thursday afternoon. The court also fined him Tk 20,000. According to the case details, Samad found the victim, daughter of a farmer from Dhamrai Upazila, alone and violated her on June 21, 2007 at around 3pm. The victim's mother found her covered in blood when she returned from work. A case was filed with the Dhamrai Police Station in this connection. The police arrested Samad on Sep 12 that same year. The court took evidence from 10 people during the trial. Samad was present when the verdict was given. bdne
